Watch the betting on the first timers DEEP SEEKER and KIR ROYALE as they can win on debut.

PREVIEW.PREVIEW_COMMENT: ONE AWAY has shown very good form in his new yard over this distance and does look the one that they all have to try and beat. SEATTLE SWING bounced back to form on the turf last time out and tries it a lot further. RUSH IN is in good form and could like this course and distance. The battle for a stake cheque could be competitive and STREAK could be on of those involved.

OCHONCAR has shown guts in last tow wins and it will not be a surprise were he to win again. BLARNEY BAY makes his local debut.

BETTING.BETTING_FORECAST: 1-1 BEATABOUTTHEBUSH; 5-1 TREIZE; 7-1 SILVAN JAZZ; 10-1 PEONIE ROCK, MONEY PENNY, TYCOON CHIEF, AGTERSKOT; 12-1 AND UPWARDS OTHERS.

COMMENT.COMMENT_COMMENT: Ran on late when 18/1 and 5th of 8 runners, 3.25 lengths behind BEATABOUTTHEBUSH over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Capable of doing better.
Hanging-comfortable when 1/1 and 1st of 8 runners, 0.75 lengths ahead BEATABOUTTHEBUSH over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Good filly - hard to beat.
Ran on late when 4/1 and 5th of 11 runners, 3.10 lengths behind ROGUE RUNNER over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 04 January 17. Ran R2 Fairviewpoly 13 Ja.
Led - tired late when 5/1 and 5th of 10 runners, 5.25 lengths behind TRICIA DUPONT over 1600m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Distance suited - respect.
Backed - got up when 9/2 and 1st of 10 runners, 0.05 lengths ahead MONEY PENNY over 1300m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 23 December 16. Improving - has a chance.
Slow - not striding when 7/1 and 12th of 12 runners, 18.00 lengths behind NIKKI over 1400m at VAAL on 13 September 16. Rested - changed yards.
Steadied 200m when 33/10 and 3rd of 10 runners, 0.75 lengths behind ACROSS THE LAKE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Fair form - can place.
Baulked 400-250m when 22/1 and 12th of 17 runners, 9.35 lengths behind BEATABOUTTHEBUSH over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 21 November 16. Needs improvement to win.
Awkward on turn when 33/1 and 8th of 11 runners, 10.10 lengths behind INTISARA over 1300m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 23 December 16. Poor local runs.
Ran on late when 8/1 and 6th of 14 runners, 4.35 lengths behind VANDA over 1200m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 30 December 16. Needs to do more to win.

PREVIEW.PREVIEW_COMMENT: The Alan Greeff trained BEATABOUTTHEBUSH has done very little wrong and in fact has won all three of her starts to date. They were all achieved by small margins but maybe she is just one of those types that just pull out what is needed to win. She does take a step up in distance so will race around the turn for the first time but that may not trouble her. TREIZE could run well.

COMMENT.COMMENT_COMMENT: Always trailing when 50/1 and 14th of 16 runners, 7.80 lengths behind WILLIAM LONGSWORD over 1600m at KENILWORTH on 17 December 16. Big chance despite weight.
Faded from 400m when 16/1 and 6th of 8 runners, 9.75 lengths behind OUR ICON over 1300m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 30 December 16. Needs to improve to win.
Not striding out when 6/1 and 13th of 13 runners, 18.85 lengths behind O TAMARA over 1400m at FAIRVIEW on 08 July 16. Rested - chance if fit.
Good late progress when 15/1 and 3rd of 12 runners, 2.50 lengths behind CARDINAL over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 18 November 16. Fair form - can place.
Nervous - got up when 7/1 and 1st of 14 runners, 0.05 lengths ahead IN FULL REGALIA over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. In good form - respect.
Pace - no extra when 5/2 and 2nd of 8 runners, 2.25 lengths behind OUR ICON over 1300m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 30 December 16. Just needed local debut.
Steadied 200m when 16/1 and 8th of 14 runners, 5.80 lengths behind BOLLEMAKIESIE over 1400m at FAIRVIEW on 04 January 17. Unreliable - can upset.
Got up late when 9/2 and 1st of 11 runners, 0.10 lengths ahead ROGUE RUNNER over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 04 January 17. Ran R2 Fairviewpoly 13 Ja.

PREVIEW.PREVIEW_COMMENT: PACIFIC SPIRIT is clearly a decent horse and may have just tackled too strong a company by running in the Cape Guineas. He was not disgraced and could bounce back to winning form. In order for him to do that though he will need to give weight away to all his rivals. IN FULL REGALIA is doing well in this yard and is well suited to this course and distance.

BETTING.BETTING_FORECAST: 6-1 SWEETCHILD O MINE; 7-1 LINDA HONEY, GUCCI REBEL; 12-1 AND UPWARDS OTHERS.

COMMENT.COMMENT_COMMENT: Faded last 200m when 7/2 and 5th of 11 runners, 6.00 lengths behind SOUTH SIDE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Ignore last run - chance.
Kept going well when 6/1 and 1st of 14 runners, 0.50 lengths ahead THORNBIRD over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Improving-one to respect.
Just kept going when 22/1 and 1st of 10 runners, 0.25 lengths ahead ACROSS THE LAKE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Surprise winner of latest.
Examined - normal when 9/1 and 14th of 14 runners, 24.10 lengths behind THORNBIRD over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Battling to find her best.
Coughing when 16/1 and 14th of 15 runners, 8.50 lengths behind MOVIE SHOW over 1000m at VAAL CLASSIC on 27 October 16. Rested - changed yards.
Blood in mouth when 13/1 and 5th of 15 runners, 3.60 lengths behind LEOPARD ORCHID over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 02 December 16. Should be in the shake-up.
Drew away late when 40/1 and 1st of 17 runners, 1.25 lengths ahead GUCCI REBEL over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 28 October 16. Rested after maiden win.
Lost 1L - lame when 9/1 and 10th of 11 runners, 13.60 lengths behind SOUTH SIDE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Unreliable - can place.
Handy, weak finish when 18/1 and 8th of 8 runners, 6.05 lengths behind FORTISSIMUS over 1400m at KENILWORTH on 26 November 16. Changed yards - watch.
Nervous - no finish when 9/1 and 7th of 11 runners, 8.35 lengths behind SOUTH SIDE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Capable of an upset.
Spread a shoe when 15/1 and 12th of 14 runners, 12.85 lengths behind THORNBIRD over 1200m at FAIRVIEW on 19 December 16. Unreliable - might place.
Kept going well when 33/10 and 1st of 16 runners, 1.50 lengths ahead NOORDHOEK'S SPEED over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 02 December 16. Recent maiden winner.
Led - stopped late when 12/1 and 7th of 14 runners, 4.60 lengths behind VANDA over 1200m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 30 December 16. Only tired late last time.
No strong kick when 5/1 and 5th of 15 runners, 3.25 lengths behind MOVIE SHOW over 1000m at VAAL CLASSIC on 27 October 16. Rested - changed yards.
Hanging 800m-brushe when 18/1 and 6th of 10 runners, 2.25 lengths behind ACROSS THE LAKE over 1000m at FAIRVIEW on 09 December 16. Needs to do a bit more.
No finish when 16/1 and 7th of 13 runners, 4.10 lengths behind ALL OVER THE WORLD over 1400m at VAAL on 17 November 16. Rested - changed yards.
No extra last 400m when 8/1 and 4th of 11 runners, 3.85 lengths behind INTISARA over 1300m at FAIRVIEW POLYTRACK on 23 December 16. Fair form - can place.

PREVIEW.PREVIEW_COMMENT: A very open looking race. SWEETCHILD O MINE is capable of winning but does give weight away to all her opposition. THORNBIRD won a nice race last time out. ACROSS THE LAKE is track and trip suited. LINDA HONEY makes he debut for the Strydom yard and it may be noteworthy that Gavin Lerena has the ride. GUCCI REBEL won well on her local debut. BLACK JADE can earn some money.
